metadata.name: Engagement
metadata.description:
This collection tries to depict the fictional scenario what would happen to the terms of our NFT Art space when the artists would no longer be present?  
Without the artists, the terms that once danced in the space become meaningless and listless. The magic that brought them to life is gone, leaving behind a mere shadow of the past. It is a mournful cause, plunging the space into a pit of loneliness and melancholy.  
These terms were once the foundation of a thriving community of artists, collectors, and enthusiasts, but now they are but echoes, a lost and lonely strife. They serve as a sad reminder of what once was but now is no more. 
It is essential to remember that the heart of art lies in the artists themselves. They are the ones who breathe life into their creations, and without them, the NFT space would be a hollow shell.
